312
00:24:55,321 --> 00:24:59,274
You made a movie with
no animation, no stunts,

313
00:24:59,341 --> 00:25:02,577
no cars that transform into stuff,

314
00:25:02,628 --> 00:25:05,079
no aliens, and no rabbits.

315
00:25:05,130 --> 00:25:06,414
Yes, I did.

316
00:25:06,465 --> 00:25:08,883
What the heck else is there?

317
00:25:08,950 --> 00:25:10,501
Romance?

318
00:25:10,569 --> 00:25:13,588
I don't think anyone wants to see that.

319
00:25:13,639 --> 00:25:15,506
Yeah.

320
00:25:15,574 --> 00:25:19,126
I'm not sure anyone
wants to buy it, either.

321
00:25:19,178 --> 00:25:20,545
Here.

322
00:25:20,612 --> 00:25:22,230
It helped my mom.

323
00:25:22,297 --> 00:25:25,400
It's good luck. You're gonna need it.

324
00:25:25,467 --> 00:25:28,820
What do you know? You're 6,
and you're drinking at a bar.

325
00:25:30,939 --> 00:25:32,440
7.

326
00:25:32,491 --> 00:25:34,475
Nice.

327
00:25:34,526 --> 00:25:38,229
Nice work, el borracho.

328
00:25:38,297 --> 00:25:41,949
