426
00:34:23,769 --> 00:34:25,353
Well...

427
00:34:25,421 --> 00:34:28,089
The next thing I want to
do is ask you to be my wife

428
00:34:28,157 --> 00:34:31,343
and tell you how much I love you

429
00:34:31,410 --> 00:34:34,312
